                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250407-158-victim868 t18250407-158-viclabel852"></join>. I was coming out of the room adjoining the shop, and saw the prisoner take a boot off a nail; he was looking at it; as I thought he did not want to buy, I watched him; saw him take the other; put both into his apron and walk off - I overtook him a dozen yards off with them; he said he took them because there was another person by who would if he had not - he then said he was drunk, and that he was happier in Newgate then out of it.</p>
